{"tid":1000035,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"節外生枝新毒計","createTime":"2019-01-29T06:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T09:51:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c4bc0d44f0654c60b621b2bcb343e346fea4d45","tid":1000035,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190129/20601065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F20601065&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=8e8347a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F20601065&h=3a0e19e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190129/20601065</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月29日 <br />\n<br />\n節外生枝新毒計 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190129/large/e8804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190129%2Flarge%2Fe8804a.jpg&h=4b2a5b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n歲末人人都很忙碌，誰知那什麼「妖道」，銅鑼灣灣仔中環&hellip;&hellip;塞到個個躁狂症。香港交通擠塞問題，由成事不足敗事有餘的低能妹仔「解決」？花了幾百億還差過以前，她巴巴的北上拜會權貴游說的「三隧分流」，得不夠票支持，又死死地氣擱置，人唔笑狗都吠。<br />\n<br />\n朝令夕改的不止一兩單，而是單單：為了面子不甘依循薯片叔叔之簡易派錢法，人人$6,000皆大歡喜，777與劏房波偏偏把$4,000派得晦氣又賤格，複雜擾民，天怒人怨。僭建驊其身不正當然要聽令放生689 UGL案，但歪理謬論極難服眾。好了， 777與陰陽怪氣的羅致光公公，兩奴攜手提高長者綜援門檻，以為「補鑊金」$1,060已算跪低──誰知忽見節外生枝新毒計，就是60至64歲長者須參與就業援助計劃，若不搵工做，社署會扣綜援金$200！這是什麼冷血政府？林鄭諂媚上位，狐假虎威，沒有一項政策措施是為香港和港人福祉着想，只求淘空萬億庫存利益輸送予主子，如今欺老虐老罰老，還連少少$200也不放過？除了「折墮」，找不到任何形容詞。就算再跪低擱置，已暴露其陰毒。<br />\n<br />\n白襪仔先生，你何時大振夫綱？把禍港殃民令祖宗蒙羞的林門鄭氏回收，好生訓誨教導，造福人群，以免港人陪葬。  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n比宮鬥更可怕 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n垃圾箱不環保嗎？ (李純恩)"},{"pid":"b6cf4d06a9ef83f3191d648cc0fe9afdd286034e","tid":1000035,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156860536712357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156860536712357&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=5c098565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156860536712357</a>"}]}